entries.category: The Clone Relics, Fist of the Empire
entries.journal_entry_description: You stumbled upon classified Rebel data. Things can only get better from here on... or can they?
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The Imperial base is under attack by the Rebel scum. Help defend it!
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: The foolish Rebels are attacking the base. Defend the Empire and defeat them all!
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: The attack seems to be over. You should return to Admiral Krieg.
